subject: Colleges and Universities
Rowing
lead_paragraph: California-Berkeley defeated Georgetown by four and a half lengths in the most lopsided of four quarterfinals yesterday, and it led three other United States teams into the semifinals of the Temple Cup at the Henley Royal Regatta in England. The Cal crew will now race Brown. Colgate and Cornell will meet in the other semifinal.
